---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Moana Live Action"
  description="Privacy policy for moana-live-action.online. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website."
  keywords="moana live action privacy policy, website privacy policy"
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to moana-live-action.online ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website. Please read this privacy policy carefully. By using our website, you accept the terms of this policy.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>2.1 Information Automatically Collected</h3>
        <p>When you access our website, we may automatically collect certain information about your device and browsing activity, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>Referring URLs</li>
          <li>Pages viewed and time spent on pages</li>
          <li>Date and time of visits</li>
          <li>Click patterns</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 Google Analytics</h3>
        <p>We use Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google, Inc. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect information about how visitors use our website. This information is used to compile reports and improve our website. Google may also transfer this information to third parties where required by law. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

        <h3>2.3 Cookies</h3>
        <p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small data files stored on your device. We use cookies for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analytics (understanding how visitors interact with our site)</li>
          <li>Advertising (displaying relevant ads through third-party services)</li>
          <li>Functionality (remembering your preferences)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect certain features of our website.</p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party services on our website, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> May use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Collects usage data as described above.</li>
          <li><strong>Amazon Associates:</strong> When you click on affiliate links and make purchases, Amazon may collect information as per their own privacy policy.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Affiliate Links & Advertising</h2>
        <p>Our website contains affiliate links to third-party products and services (such as Amazon). If you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. These third-party services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites.</p>

        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child under 13, please contact us so we can promptly remove it.</p>

        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.</p>

        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of data collection through cookies</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>

        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@moana-live-action.online">contact@moana-live-action.online</a></li>
          <li>Website: <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a></li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077be 0%, #00d4aa 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .page-header p { opacity: 0.9; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: white;
  }
  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .content-wrapper h2 {
    color: var(--dark);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper h3 {
    color: var(--dark);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper li {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
